      "markdownsSource": "content",
      "markdownValue": "```contributionGraph\ntitle: 阅读打卡\ngraphType: calendar\ndateRangeValue: 1\ndateRangeType: LATEST_MONTH\nstartOfWeek: 1\nshowCellRuleIndicators: true\ntitleStyle:\n  textAlign: center\n  fontSize: 20px\n  fontWeight: normal\ndataSource:\n  type: TASK_IN_SPECIFIC_PAGE\n  value: '\"03_输出_每日日记\"'\n  dateField:\n    type: FILE_CTIME\n    value: \"\"\n  filters:\n    - id: \"1758152172068\"\n      type: STATUS_IS\n      value: COMPLETED\n    - id: \"1758156214813\"\n      type: CONTAINS_ANY_TAG\n      value:\n        - \"#习惯/阅读\"\nfillTheScreen: true\nenableMainContainerShadow: false\ncellStyleRules:\n  - id: 1758152432435\n    min: \"0\"\n    max: \"1\"\n    color: \"#a8cedcff\"\n    text: \"\"\n  - id: 1758152439027\n    min: \"1\"\n    max: 2\n    color: \"#45c8d5ff\"\n    text: ✨\ncellStyle:\n  minWidth: 25px\n  minHeight: 25px\nmainContainerStyle: {}\n\n```",
