      "markdownsSource": "content",
      "markdownValue": "```contributionGraph\ntitle: 待办（模型）打卡\ngraphType: calendar\ndateRangeValue: 1\ndateRangeType: LATEST_MONTH\nstartOfWeek: 1\nshowCellRuleIndicators: true\ntitleStyle:\n  textAlign: center\n  fontSize: 20px\n  fontWeight: normal\ndataSource:\n  type: TASK_IN_SPECIFIC_PAGE\n  value: '\"03_输出_每日日记\"'\n  dateField:\n    type: TASK_PROPERTY\n    value: completion\n  filters:\n    - id: \"1758152172068\"\n      type: STATUS_IS\n      value: COMPLETED\n    - id: \"1758156214813\"\n      type: CONTAINS_ANY_TAG\n      value:\n        - \"#习惯/日记\"\nfillTheScreen: true\nenableMainContainerShadow: false\ncellStyleRules:\n  - id: Ocean_a\n    color: \"#8dd1e2\"\n    min: 1\n    max: 2\n  - id: Ocean_b\n    color: \"#63a1be\"\n    min: 2\n    max: 3\ncellStyle:\n  minWidth: 64px\n  minHeight: 64px\n  borderRadius: 50%\n\n```\n",
      "title": "待办模型打卡"
    },
